      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FREYA LEGEND (1) boasts strong form at this course and distance having won three times from three starts. Placed last time (19.58) at Murray Bridge in a Grade 6, finishing second and beaten 1.3 lengths. With a clean break looks hard to beat. GOLDIE RUSTY (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at this track in a handy 17.38 beating Bristol Moss. Has performed well from this box with a win and five minor placings to her name from eight starts. Sure to measure up. GETTING CHEEKY (4) boasts a consistent overall record including five wins from 21 starts, the latest hitting the minor money when third (19.81) over 350m at Murray Bridge. Has a good record here at this journey. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. CERISE (8) racing over this course and distance brings the best out in her.",
